mxTextCell.label: *In the online version of Machinations, State Connections cannot act as triggers on Resource/State Connections. Therefore, this version of the Pac-Man example (from “Game Mechanics: Advance Game Design”, Adams, Dormans, 2012) is updated to reflect this change.
